        "text_waxcLB": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Removing moisture and wrinkles from the product is not necessary with Ninja Transfers. Only do a prepress if you prefer.</p><p></p><p><strong>Pro Tip:</strong> If you’re pressing onto a garment or surface you haven’t worked with before, we recommend doing a small test press first to confirm the settings and ensure the best results.</p>",
