        },
        "text_yCY8Pr": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Position your transfer in the desired location and make sure it is flat before pressing. You can press across seams, for example on 6-panel hats and side seams of t-shirts. Heat-resistant tape is recommended when pressing on hats or when using a household iron to prevent the transfer from moving. You'll learn when it's needed with experience.</p>",
